When Our Company processes your order, we may send your data to and also use the resulting information from credit reference agencies to prevent fraudulent purchases.
How do we store your data?
Our Company securely stores your data at a data processing centre.
Our Company will keep your data for 7 years. Once this time period has expired, we will delete your data by encrypting it.
Marketing
Our Company would like to send you information about products and services of ours that we think you might like, as well as those of our partner companies.
